Best Answer: Firstly, not all animals that group have a specific name, in these cases, they are just called 'groups'. It is not automatic, therefore, that panthers would have their own term anyway. Secondly, many group names are rather obscure and have no underlying basis for the name, they are quite arbitrarily applied.
